Cell["\<\
Small section to derive the analytic expressions relevant for the spectrum \
computation\
\>", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.946380157694522*^9, 
  3.946380188790737*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"856af46f-6bc5-4c86-b0cb-\
